-- User guide --

1, requirements
- mongodb 
- python 3.4.3 with pyenv
  * pip install pillow
  * pip install pymongo
  * pip install pdf2image
  * pip install Flask-PyMongo
  * pip install python-dateutil 
(- python 2 with pyenv)

2, preparetion
 > 1, git clone this source
      git clone https://gitlab.cern.ch/akubota/web-app-db-yarr.git
 > 2, modify some points
      in app.py
        app.config["MONGO_URI"] = "mongodb://<IP address>:<port>/<dbName>" 
        * IP address : "localhost" or IP address of server with mongodb
        * port : TCP port used by mongodb (default:27017)
        * dbName : select database to show
       
        app.run(host='<IP address>')
        * IP address : "127.0.0.1" or IP address of server with mongodb
 > 3, run 
      <in running mongodb>
      pyenv local 3.4.3
      python app.py
      
